description: Dragon dogs are the tastiest Hot dogs in Orange County, We've been business for 13 years and have big fan club.One of the most famous dogs is DUI a bacon wrap dog covered with Chili/Cheese,Pastrami,Grilled Onion and along w/all the fixings.We specialize in Hot dogs varies types but are also known for TRI- TIP sandwiches and smoked pull pork,Hawaiian food (Bacon Fried Rice is a Fav" of customers and Teriyaki Chicken is a must too try.And our Tacos are the best marinade mouth watering tacos in town. This is a Mom n Pop and family owned business is with nothing but love in every bite of food.Everyone knows Matt aka Know as Hot Dog Guy in Orange County,Good Guy and best comforting food ever,it hits the spot very time.
name: Dragon Dogs
